---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="Mental Health Care | Medical Care and Rehabilitation"
  description="Explore mental health care services available to UK veterans through the Armed Forces Compensation Scheme. Learn about treatment options, support programmes, and resources for mental wellbeing.">
  <div class="container my-5">
    <h1 class="display-4 mb-4">Mental Health Care for Veterans</h1>
    <div class="row g-4">
      <div class="col-lg-8">
        <p class="lead">The Armed Forces Compensation Scheme (AFCS) recognises the importance of mental health care for veterans. This page outlines the comprehensive mental health services and support available to help you maintain and improve your mental wellbeing.</p>
        
        <h2 class="h3 mt-4">Assessment and Diagnosis</h2>
        <p>Our mental health assessment services include:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Comprehensive psychological evaluations</li>
          <li>PTSD screening and diagnosis</li>
          <li>Assessment for depression, anxiety, and other mental health conditions</li>
          <li>Neuropsychological testing for cognitive issues</li>
        </ul>
        
        <h2 class="h3 mt-4">Treatment Options</h2>
        <p>We offer a range of evidence-based treatments:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Cognitive Behavioural Therapy (CBT)</li>
          <li>Eye Movement Desensitization and Reprocessing (EMDR) for PTSD</li>
          <li>Medication management with psychiatric support</li>
          <li>Group therapy sessions</li>
          <li>Mindfulness and stress reduction techniques</li>
        </ul>
        
        <h2 class="h3 mt-4">Specialised PTSD Programmes</h2>
        <p>Dedicated support for Post-Traumatic Stress Disorder:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Intensive PTSD treatment programmes</li>
          <li>Trauma-focused therapies</li>
          <li>Residential treatment options for severe cases</li>
          <li>Family support and education about PTSD</li>
        </ul>
        
        <h2 class="h3 mt-4">Substance Abuse Support</h2>
        <p>Comprehensive care for substance use disorders:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Detoxification programmes</li>
          <li>Rehabilitation services</li>
          <li>Ongoing support groups and counselling</li>
          <li>Dual diagnosis treatment for co-occurring mental health issues</li>
        </ul>
        
        <h2 class="h3 mt-4">Peer Support and Group Therapy</h2>
        <p>Opportunities to connect with fellow veterans:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Peer-led support groups</li>
          <li>Structured group therapy sessions</li>
          <li>Online forums and virtual support communities</li>
          <li>Mentoring programmes</li>
        </ul>
        
        <h2 class="h3 mt-4">Family and Relationship Counselling</h2>
        <p>Support for maintaining healthy relationships:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Couples therapy</li>
          <li>Family counselling sessions</li>
          <li>Parenting support for veterans</li>
          <li>Education programmes for family members</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="col-lg-4">
        <div class="card bg-light mb-4">
          <div class="card-body">
            <h3 class="h5">Related Services</h3>
            <ul class="list-unstyled">
              <li><a href="/medical/rehabilitation" class="text-decoration-none">Rehabilitation Services</a></li>
              <li><a href="/support/career-transition" class="text-decoration-none">Career Transition Support</a></li>
              <li><a href="/financial/budgeting" class="text-decoration-none">Financial Planning</a></li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="card mb-4">
          <div class="card-body">
            <h3 class="h5">Mental Health Helpline</h3>
            <p>For immediate mental health support, contact our 24/7 helpline.</p>
            <p class="fw-bold">0800 XXX XXXX</p>
            <a href="/mental-health-support" class="btn btn-primary">Learn More</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
